	⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠉⠀⠈⢣⡀⠀⠀⢇⠀⢻⣦⣸⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢀⣇⡰⡿⠀⠰⠁⠀⢀⡜⠁⠀⠉⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀\n\
